  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 20th Level you gain two ranks of Expertise in every skill or tool you are already proficient in.</p><p> Additionally you gain Proficiency in every Skill, Saving Throw or Toolkit you aren't Proficient in.</p><p> Additionally your Versatile Expert feature now gives expertise in the chosen skills or tool kits.</p><p> Lastly, spending Superiority Die on Skill Checks does not consume them anymore.</p><p></p>",
